    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BGMOBA is a team-vs-team battle game where two teams of 16 players fight for control of objective points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Station</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/77d929a22f07dc30bb21099a0f5a0a8d.avif?t=1757347841\" width=616 height=315 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Station is the lobby of the game. It's a flying fortress where you hang out in between battles. Here you can meet other players and practice for battle by fighting against NPCs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/38f349530fc96830371394d312036446.webp?t=1757347841\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/38f349530fc96830371394d312036446.poster.webp?t=1757347841\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=273 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/87b0d0ddc3825ecb9c28f0a6b7787310.webp?t=1757347841\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/87b0d0ddc3825ecb9c28f0a6b7787310.poster.webp?t=1757347841\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=273 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battles take place on the planet beneath The Station. Here you'll fight for control of mining drills that generate points for your team. Battles last between 10 and 20 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/31db005f2d30197241c386ec558a9489.webp?t=1757347841\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/31db005f2d30197241c386ec558a9489.poster.webp?t=1757347841\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=273 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/457c8677bfa89fb47e7e00365c2fe889.webp?t=1757347841\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/457c8677bfa89fb47e7e00365c2fe889.poster.webp?t=1757347841\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=273 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 9 classes in BGMOBA, each with a unique playstyle and role on the battlefield. You can freely switch between them when in safe zone or after dying and resurrecting in a battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/3bd8a1385ad02c9541f703a26db4ae80.avif?t=1757347841\" width=616 height=383 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hammerhead</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Melee] [Damage-dealer]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A powerful melee class that does heavy single-target damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/dd4f5550f562765c578c52525296c239.avif?t=1757347841\" width=616 height=383 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Medic</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Ranged] [Healer]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A healer with strong single-target healing spells.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/e1a627eb33926d123ace318c1c58e840.avif?t=1757347841\" width=616 height=383 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deadeye</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Ranged [Damage-dealer]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long-ranged single-target DPS class that takes out people from afar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/67722425fa76955ea56395b0adb90607.avif?t=1757347841\" width=616 height=383 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Symbiot</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Melee] [Damage-dealer/Healer Hybrid]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A durable tank-like class who heals allies and damages enemies through AoE effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/c33eca22e763b2539a90a3a5c49f9611.avif?t=1757347841\" width=616 height=383 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bomber</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Ranged] [Damage-dealer]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long-raged multi-target DPS class with explosive AoE attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/77febc7f8923d09e80f8ecf5e2bd7212.avif?t=1757347841\" width=616 height=383 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Ranged/Melee Hybrid] [Damage-dealer]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A swift semi-ranged DPS class that specializes in damage-over-time effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/aa9d80ccf5773ec90065be86e7e2e0c7.avif?t=1757347841\" width=616 height=383 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Infuser</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Ranged] [Healer]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An elusive healer that specializes in heal-over-time effects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/3003da53a877d0a6a6ab1a969096c210.avif?t=1757347841\" width=616 height=383 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reaper</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Melee] [Damage-dealer]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A melee class that focuses on debuffing enemies and reducing healing they take.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259770/extras/52a484171e1da9816a141f670e408cb3.avif?t=1757347841\" width=616 height=383 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Copycat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Super Hybrid]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A class that can transform itself temporarily into any other class.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
